Received: from Majordom by mailserv.mta.ca with local (Exim 4.61)
	(envelope-from <cat-dist@mta.ca>)
	id 1IesOJ-0003xO-Tr
	for categories-list@mta.ca; Mon, 08 Oct 2007 10:11:24 -0300
Date: Sun, 07 Oct 2007 16:20:42 -0700
From: Vaughan Pratt <pratt@cs.stanford.edu>
MIME-Version: 1.0
To: Categories list <categories@mta.ca>
Subject: categories: Re: Help!
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-1; format=flowed
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
Sender: cat-dist@mta.ca
Precedence: bulk
Message-Id: <E1IesOJ-0003xO-Tr@mailserv.mta.ca>
Status: O
