From: Juergen Koslowski <koslowj@iti.cs.tu-bs.de>
Subject: categories: CT07, please help identifying more participants!
To: categories@mta.ca (categories list)
Date: Tue, 16 Oct 2007 13:56:02 +0200 (CEST)
